@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Level 1
title US 2.2.1 - Create, Update and Search Vessel Types

participant "REST Client" as Client
participant "Backend API" as API

== Create Vessel Type ==

Client -> API : POST /api/vesseltypes\nBody: { name, description, capacity, constraints }
API --> Client : 201 Created\nBody: { id, name, description, capacity, constraints }

== Update Vessel Type ==

Client -> API : PUT /api/vesseltypes/{id}\nBody: { updated fields }
API --> Client : 200 OK\nBody: { id, name, description, capacity, constraints }

== Search Vessel Types ==

Client -> API : GET /api/vesseltypes?search={text}
API --> Client : 200 OK\nBody: [ { id, name, description, ... }, ... ]

@enduml
